data.chText: 用真空吸尘器清扫（地毯、地板等）
data.enText: to clean a carpet, floor, etc. with a vacuum cleaner

data.chText: 用真空吸尘器把…清除掉
data.enText: to remove sth from a carpet, floor, etc. with a vacuum cleaner

data.chText: 用吸尘器清除所有的灰尘
data.enText: to hoover up all the dust
to get or collect sth in large quantities

data.chText: 美国和加拿大通常夺得大部分的金牌。
data.enText: The US and Canada usually hoover up most of the gold medals.
It's your turn to do the hoovering .

value.def: If you hoover a room or a carpet, you clean it using a vacuum cleaner.

example.ex: She hoovered the study and the sitting-room.
example.tran: 她用吸尘器打扫了书房和客厅。

example.ex: I finished off the hoovering upstairs.
example.tran: 我完成了楼上的吸尘打扫工作。
